on New Year's Eve

01:18.208 --> 01:19.557
than my father ever was.

01:20.732 --> 01:21.951
That's the third time
this month.

01:21.994 --> 01:23.387
- I'll call the super.

01:23.431 --> 01:26.782
- It's just--
it's so thoughtless.

01:28.088 --> 01:30.960
- I'll call first thing
in the morning.

01:31.003 --> 01:33.093
- Ugh.

01:34.050 --> 01:37.445
- Come on.
Let's make this quick.

01:37.488 --> 01:39.882
Come on.

01:43.277 --> 01:45.279
Okay, come on.

02:02.209 --> 02:03.862
- Hey, Gavin?

02:03.906 --> 02:06.430
We're out of shampoo.

02:06.474 --> 02:09.825
I can't find my hairbrush.

02:09.868 --> 02:10.956
No!

02:12.219 --> 02:13.829
No! Gavin!

02:13.872 --> 02:15.004
No, no!

02:15.047 --> 02:16.266
Get off of me!

02:16.310 --> 02:18.138
Gavin!

02:18.181 --> 02:20.270
Gavin!

02:20.314 --> 02:22.272
No!

02:22.316 --> 02:25.057
Please!

02:25.101 --> 02:26.537
No, no, please!

02:26.581 --> 02:29.018
Please stop!

02:39.159 --> 02:40.943
I screamed,

02:40.986 --> 02:42.684
and I-I tried to run,

02:42.727 --> 02:45.469
but he, um,
threw me on the bed

02:45.513 --> 02:47.819
and he tied me up,
and he, um--

02:47.863 --> 02:49.169
he r-raped me.

02:49.212 --> 02:51.301
- I'm so, so, so, so sorry,

02:51.345 --> 02:53.173
and we're gonna get you
to the hospital.

02:53.216 --> 02:54.478
- I just knew
something terrible

02:54.522 --> 02:55.914
was gonna happen tonight,
I just knew it.

02:55.958 --> 02:57.525
- Okay, you said that
he wore a ski mask.

02:57.568 --> 02:59.222
Do you remember
anything else about his--

02:59.266 --> 03:01.093
about his height or his build?

03:01.137 --> 03:02.791
He--he was average.

03:02.834 --> 03:05.141
I-I think he--
I think he was white.

03:05.185 --> 03:06.795
- Okay, and is there anything
else that you remember?

03:06.838 --> 03:09.319
Anything that he said,
anything at all?

03:09.363 --> 03:11.278
Um, he--he told me

03:11.321 --> 03:13.280
to be quiet.

03:13.323 --> 03:15.325
He said that if I--
I screamed again,

03:15.369 --> 03:17.022
that he would--
he would kill Gavin!

03:17.066 --> 03:19.329
- Okay, let's get you
to the hospital, okay?

03:19.373 --> 03:21.462
- Okay, come on.

03:21.505 --> 03:24.204
You're gonna be okay.
- I was at the kitchen sink.

03:24.247 --> 03:26.858
Felt a knife
at the back of my neck.

03:26.902 --> 03:28.817
- Any idea how he got in?

03:28.860 --> 03:31.385
- We--we just got home
from the holidays.

03:31.428 --> 03:34.083
