was propped open.

03:34.126 --> 03:35.389
I-I thought there was
something off

03:35.432 --> 03:36.694
about our doorknob.

03:36.738 --> 03:38.174
- Okay, you didn't see
his face.

03:38.218 --> 03:39.828
Anything about his voice?

03:39.871 --> 03:41.960
- It was--was low.

03:42.004 --> 03:43.353
Creepy.

03:43.397 --> 03:45.790
He said to lay on the floor.

03:45.834 --> 03:47.357
Tied me up.

03:47.401 --> 03:50.230
Stacked plates on my back.

03:50.273 --> 03:52.362
He said if I moved he'd hear

03:52.406 --> 03:55.191
and April was dead.

03:55.235 --> 03:57.454
- Okay.

03:59.935 --> 04:01.328
- Fin.

04:01.371 --> 04:02.764
So April Baker says

04:02.807 --> 04:04.418
the attack happened
around midnight.

04:04.461 --> 04:06.028
She managed to free herself--

04:06.071 --> 04:07.725
untie herself
three hours later.

04:07.769 --> 04:10.554
- Husband says son of a bitch
stacked plates on his back.

04:10.598 --> 04:12.208
- So while he's raping her,

04:12.252 --> 04:13.905
he can hear
if the husband moved.

04:13.949 --> 04:15.255
- Exactly.

04:15.298 --> 04:17.605
- Let's get inside.

04:17.648 --> 04:19.781
- So whoever did this
disassembled the door latch

04:19.824 --> 04:21.391
then jerry-rigged it
back together

04:21.435 --> 04:23.175
so that nobody would notice.

04:23.219 --> 04:24.916
- The perp staked out the place
when they were out of town?

04:24.960 --> 04:25.917
- We're looking at a pro.

04:25.961 --> 04:28.442
- Maybe worse.

04:35.492 --> 04:38.321
- Is this for real?

04:38.365 --> 04:39.888
- Surveilling the apartment,

04:39.931 --> 04:41.759
breaking the door lock,
stacking plates.

04:41.803 --> 04:43.892
- I didn't want
to believe it either.

04:43.935 --> 04:45.981
How long has it been?

04:46.024 --> 04:48.679
- Twenty-five years.

04:52.030 --> 04:55.295
The Infinity Rapist.

05:43.125 --> 05:46.824
- So Infinity's last rape
was January 2, 1994.

05:46.868 --> 05:48.652
I was a rookie
in the five-five.

05:48.696 --> 05:51.176
Everyone in the five Boroughs
knew about that case.

05:51.220 --> 05:53.396
- Uh, not so much in Georgia.
How many rapes was he good for?

05:53.440 --> 05:56.486
- Twenty-two, in Manhattan
and Brooklyn from '81 to '94.

05:56.530 --> 05:58.053
This guy targeted couples.

05:58.096 --> 05:59.968
He'd case out the place,
jimmy open a door or window.

06:00.011 --> 06:01.839
Then he'd lie in wait,
break in a second time.

06:01.883 --> 06:03.624
- He'd tie up the boyfriend
or husband,

06:03.667 --> 06:05.277
then he'd stack plates
on their back

06:05.321 --> 06:07.671
and he said if he heard
a rattle, the woman was dead.

06:07.715 --> 06:09.717
- He took trophies.
Small personal items.

06:09.760 --> 06:11.849
After the fifth rape,
he started leaving messages.

06:11.893 --> 06:13.677
"Infinity: 5.
NYPD: 0."

06:13.721 --> 06:15.287
- You, know, if this is him,

06:15.331 --> 06:17.028
he's been out of commission
for over two decades,

06:17.072 --> 06:19.466
which makes him middle-aged
or older.

06:19.509 --> 06:20.945
So do we alert Crime Stoppers?
- No.

06:20.989 --> 06:22.904
Until we know
what we're dealing with,

06:22.947 --> 06:25.863
One P.P. wants to keep it
on the "DL."

06:25.907 --> 06:29.301
- Okay, no DNA
in April's rape kit.

06:29.345 --> 06:30.868
CSU found two hairs
in the bed

06:30.912 --> 06:32.479
but they're not a match
to the Bakers

06:32.522 --> 06:34.437
and no match in CODIS.

06:34.481 --> 06:36.439
- Okay, so check that DNA
against old evidence.

06:36.483 --> 06:39.442
Have Stone do some digging.

06:42.880 --> 06:44.404
- Twenty-five years later.

06:44.447 --> 06:45.840
Did they get a sense
of this guy's age?

06:45.883 --> 06:46.623
- Uh, no.

06:46.667 --> 06:48.277
They said that he, uh--

06:48.320 --> 06:50.540
