he told the wife to keep quiet.

06:50.584 --> 06:52.063
They didn't fight back,

06:52.107 --> 06:53.456
so there's no sense
of his physicality either.

06:53.500 --> 06:56.198
- Here you go.

06:56.241 --> 06:59.680
"Infinity, '81 to '94."

06:59.723 --> 07:01.899
There's over a dozen of them.

07:01.943 --> 07:04.380
