07:12.257 --> 07:13.694
"Ben Stone,
District Attorney's Office.

07:13.737 --> 07:16.436
Joint Infinity Task Force."

07:18.263 --> 07:19.395
- I didn't know.

07:19.439 --> 07:20.483
