about his cases.

07:24.792 --> 07:27.403
- "The Infinity Rapist"?

07:27.447 --> 07:28.752
You guys think it was him?

07:28.796 --> 07:30.101
That's...

07:30.145 --> 07:31.451
Horrifying.

07:31.494 --> 07:33.104
- Well, we--we don't know
for sure, but the--

07:33.148 --> 07:36.891
