or watching your building?

07:44.115 --> 07:46.117
An older man?

07:46.161 --> 07:48.337
- No.

07:48.380 --> 07:50.600
- Okay, um...

07:50.644 --> 07:52.602
He threatened to kill Gavin.

07:52.646 --> 07:55.518
Did he say anything else
that you can remember?

07:55.562 --> 07:59.043
Anything at all.

07:59.087 --> 08:00.958
- He told me to shut up.

08:01.002 --> 08:03.004
He put his hand over my mouth

08:03.047 --> 08:07.312
like he didn't want me
to make a sound.

08:07.356 --> 08:10.315
- Did anything go missing?

08:10.359 --> 08:11.926
- No.

08:11.969 --> 08:14.189
We had cash in a desk.
