08:14.232 --> 08:16.496
- This would have been
something personal.

08:16.539 --> 08:18.889
- N-no.

08:20.369 --> 08:21.631
Uh, wait.

08:21.675 --> 08:24.242
I couldn't find my hairbrush.

08:24.286 --> 08:27.681
Does that matter?

08:27.724 --> 08:29.596
- Uh, it might.

08:29.639 --> 08:32.076
It might.

08:33.164 --> 08:35.732
- I had no idea how haunted
my father was about this case.

08:35.776 --> 08:37.386
- Yeah, a lot of people
in law enforcement

08:37.429 --> 08:38.648
lost sleep over this guy.

08:38.692 --> 08:41.869
He was like the Zodiac
or the Son of Sam.

08:41.912 --> 08:44.175
- These notations
in my father's handwriting?

08:44.219 --> 08:46.351
They're dated 2017.

08:46.395 --> 08:47.918
- That's a year before he died.

08:47.962 --> 08:50.138
- Yeah.

08:59.451 --> 09:01.671
- Hey, Carisi, look at this.

09:03.412 --> 09:05.632
- Who's this?
- That's me and my father.

09:05.675 --> 09:06.894
- How old are you here?

09:06.937 --> 09:08.373
- Uh, seven?

09:08.417 --> 09:10.158
- How'd that get in
the case file?

09:10.201 --> 09:12.595
- I don't know.

09:16.164 --> 09:19.297
- Okay, we have unmarked cars
on the Bakers' block, right?

09:19.341 --> 09:21.386
