09:26.914 --> 09:28.263
We've been going over
the old case files.

09:28.306 --> 09:30.570
Ben Stone was the lead ADA
in the case.

09:30.613 --> 09:31.832
- I didn't realize that.

09:31.875 --> 09:32.876
- And whoever attacked
the Bakers

09:32.920 --> 09:34.443
was definitely not Infinity.

09:34.486 --> 09:37.228
The signatures,
the reconnaissance, the plates.

09:37.272 --> 09:39.579
