off your face.

12:09.685 --> 12:12.470
Tell us what you did.

12:12.514 --> 12:15.778
- I've been waiting
for this moment for 25 years.

12:15.822 --> 12:17.649
I want to savor it.

12:17.693 --> 12:19.782
- I'm done.

12:21.828 --> 12:23.090
- Wait!

12:23.133 --> 12:25.614
