12:31.141 --> 12:32.490
- What about her husband?

12:32.534 --> 12:34.666
- I tied him up,
stacked plates on his back.

12:34.710 --> 12:37.800
Told him if I heard
so much as a rattle, game over.

12:37.844 --> 12:39.193
That's my signature.

12:39.236 --> 12:41.108
- Your signature?

12:41.151 --> 12:42.631
- Of course.

12:42.674 --> 12:46.200
But you knew that.

12:46.243 --> 12:49.116
- This guy laying out
his own insanity defense?

12:49.159 --> 12:50.465
- He's not doing a bad job.

12:50.508 --> 12:52.206
- Well, he can't be Infinity.

12:52.249 --> 12:54.817
Patton wasn't born until
a year after the first rape.

12:54.861 --> 12:56.123
- What's his history?

12:56.166 --> 12:58.865
- He's an unemployed
computer programmer.

12:58.908 --> 13:00.127
From his social media,

13:00.170 --> 13:02.172
