with Infinity

13:02.216 --> 13:03.521
since he was a teenager.

13:03.565 --> 13:05.219
- And we know he's good
for April and Gavin?

13:05.262 --> 13:07.874
- He planned it to commemorate
the 25th anniversary

13:07.917 --> 13:10.137
of Infinity's last rape.

13:10.180 --> 13:12.443
