14:22.078 --> 14:23.601
Claire Newbury.

14:23.645 --> 14:25.908
I interviewed
your father years ago.

14:25.952 --> 14:28.041
I've written three books
on Infinity.

14:28.084 --> 14:29.520
- Sorry, I never read them.

14:29.564 --> 14:31.392
- Oh, but you must have been
interested in his cases.

14:31.435 --> 14:32.741
Your father's white whale.

14:32.784 --> 14:34.438
